<div class="postHeader">
<ul class="clear">
<li class="postCategories">
<a href="https://breakingdefense.com/category/air/" rel="category tag">Air Warfare</a>, <a href="https://breakingdefense.com/category/sea/" rel="category tag">Naval Warfare</a>, <a href="https://breakingdefense.com/category/networks-and-cyber/" rel="category tag">Networks / Cyber</a>, <a href="https://breakingdefense.com/category/threats/" rel="category tag">Threats</a> </li>
